# Folder & filenames

When defining a component, the name of the folder and its related files should use PascalCase pattern.

```
/Button
  /Button.test.tsx
  /Button.tsx
```

When defining a utility files or a hook, the name of the folder its related files should use dash-case pattern.

```
/use-controllable-state
  /use-controllable-state.test.ts
  /use-controllable-state.ts

/constants
  /constants.ts
```